data.description: Nice 2 story home in well established neighborhood! Durable wood laminate floors, kitchen with white cabinetry, countertops and built-in desk area, sliding doors leading to the large fenced in backyard. Roomy two car garage conveniently on the main level. Upstairs has the master bedroom with an ensuite bathroom, walk in closet and additional built-in storage. Two more bedrooms and a full bathroom with updated vanity also on upper level. No HOA, easy access to Powers cooridor, Peterson SFB, Ft Carson and more.
